{"tid":1133971,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"［古典撚］古典音樂台(附入門指南","createTime":"2019-05-01T12:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T12:56:18.000Z","uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0663aa2805480cf824976a4055b2996ca1346d","tid":1133971,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"小辣: 一啲稍長既作品 但係理解唔會困難 當中都係一啲作曲家最出名既作品 <br />\n<br />\nMozart Requiem :雖然mozart 本人係寫到一半已經歸左西 但係手稿留低左足夠既線索比後人完成  冇影響作品本身既偉大  我簡左最出名同鐘意既幾個樂章 比大家簡單咁理解下呢首作品<br />\nintroitus<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DsyPhvrEzPU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDsyPhvrEzPU&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=00751fbe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DsyPhvrEzPU</a><br />\nConfutatis,lacrimosa<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjtwyZAhCcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfjtwyZAhCcs&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=035821c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjtwyZAhCcs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mhYCaQkbkyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DmhYCaQkbkyw&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=e2f1e688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mhYCaQkbkyw</a><br />\ndomine jesu <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXL8zhXCxg0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlXL8zhXCxg0&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEMF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=253d7439\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lXL8zhXCxg0</a><br />\nMozart Symphony 41 &quot;jupiter&quot; 4th movement 要數mozart最出色既交響曲同樂章好多都會話呢首 展現左mozart出色既對位法同復調技巧<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=prvBEXbnDR0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DprvBEXbnDR